From ede9da754bd9488cda96e82f59805e9a00266864 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: 456inde <indetailsgroup@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 26 Feb 2026 15:58:41 +0700
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] fix(drillmap): correct boltDirection toward cam pocket;
 add linkage validator + golden
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Fix boltDirection to point from bolt entry toward cam pocket center
  (was incorrectly set to drilling axis = INTO panel face)
- Add validateBoltPocketLinkage pure validator with dev hook
- Add debugBoltDiag utility (dev-only) for bolt→pocket diagnostics
- Add minifixRenderInvariant regression test with null guards
- Add golden snapshot test (80-point A-run INSET baseline)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
