From: 456inde <indetailsgroup@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 26 Feb 2026 16:00:09 +0700
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] feat(drillmap): add B-run dowel-only generation with
 axis-tagged keys + pairing validator
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Add B-run (width axis) dowel-only points: 4 corners × 2 positions × 2 bores = 16 points
  HORIZ face bore (Ø8×12mm) + SIDE edge bore (Ø8×18mm) at each position
- Extend pairKeyV2 with RUN_AXIS_TAG, RunAxis type, PAIR_KEY_V2_RE regex, parse-based isRunAxis()
  B-run keys: "pair2-{corner}-B-{pos}" — guaranteed anti-collision with A-run keys
- Add narrow-cabinet guard: skip B-run when widthSpan < 2× firstHoleZ (74mm)
- Add validateBRunDowelPairing pure validator + dev hook (grouped summary output)
- Add contract comment block + dev assertion for normal opposition invariant
- Update golden snapshot (80 → 96 points) and axis alignment tests (A-run filter)
- 13 new B-run generation tests + 9 validator tests + 14 pairKeyV2 format/parse tests

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
